README for slitaz-mercurial-style
================================================================================

This the template for our so famous and so used Hg repositories.

Install: /usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/mercurial/templates/slitaz

To work on it you need hgweb.cgi with it config file, Lighttpd with
CGI Python support.

To use it localy you can install the package: slitaz-mercurial-style
and use a config file that look like that:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# hgweb.config - Hg web interface configuration
#

[collections]
/home/pankso/Projects = /home/pankso/Projects

[web]
style = slitaz
allow_archive = gz bz2
baseurl = /

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
